<a
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/channel/elephants-in-the-room/"
    class="department-name">
    <h3 class="department">Elephants in the Room</h3></a>
<span
    class="hed-heading"
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2017/07/06/saudi-arabia-is-weakening-itself-and-strengthening-iran/">
    <h1 class="hed">Saudi Arabia Is Weakening Itself and Strengthening Iran</h1>
</span>
<h2 class="dek-heading">Only by working to heal the ideological, political, and military rifts in its own Arab ranks can Saudi Arabia feel secure of its position relative to Iran.</h2>
<div class="meta-data ">
    <address class="author-list">
    <span class="pre">By</span>
    <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/author/ross-harrison/"
        rel="author"
        class="author">
    Ross Harrison</a></address>
    <span class="separator">|</span>
    <time
    pubdate
    datetime="2017-07-06"
    title="July 6th, 2017"
    class="date-time">
July 6, 2017, 6:43 PM</time>
</div>




				<figure class="figure-image ">
            <span
            style="padding-bottom:66.666666666667%;
        "
                class="image-attachment -ratioscale  horizontal-orientation">
        <img
            data-sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
